data.description: Welcome to your ideal home that offers a blend of space, comfort, and endless possibilities. With four bedrooms, a spacious living room with gas fireplace, and a cozy family room with another fireplace, it's the perfect place to create lasting memories. The versatile bonus room is great as a home office or game room. The kitchen features a convenient breakfast bar, ample cupboard, and counter space. The primary bedroom includes bathroom and a walk-in closet. The expansive outdoor living area with a covered patio is perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Outside, you'll find a garden shed and outbuilding that is ideal for a workshop or storage. This property has it all – spacious living, outdoor relaxation, and room to pursue your passions.
